About
Dr. Jeffrey Lorberbaum, MD is a Doctor primarily located in Raleigh, NC. He has 21 years of experience. His specialties include Psychiatry and Neurology.                    Dr. Lorberbaum is affiliated with                            Milton S. Hershey Medical Center.
